actually is, and a shift to focusing on the benefits of progress in place o=
f fear. I=E2=80=99m trying to do that in a small way today.=C2=A0
More tangibly, a couple of examples highlight efforts to fuse optimism into=
 institutions that I=E2=80=99m following closely: The Abundance Agenda, a m=
ore optimistic plan for government, and American Dynamism, which suggests t=
hat startups can fill in where incumbents and government fall short.
